"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-sport-paris-2024-2024-0731-1462858-paris-2024-wiffen-hardly-slept-after-olympic-gold-win\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Olympic gold medallist Daniel Wiffen said he hardly slept after his 800m freestyle triumph.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 93, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-year-old Armagh manstormed the final stretchin the La Defense Arena to clinch gold in an Olympic record time last night.\", \"from\": 95, \"to\": 222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 111, \"end\": 117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armagh_GAA\", \"score\": 0.830506447198381, \"rank\": 0.20372804023384827, \"text\": \"Armagh\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armagh_GAA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armagh_GAA\"}, {\"begin\": 153, \"end\": 163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"La Defense\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After receiving his medal on the podium, Wiffen said he went straight into anti-doping and then the swim-down before treating himself to some pizza.\", \"from\": 224, \"to\": 372, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We left the pool at 12.30am, got back into the dining hall, had a couple slices of pizza, then tried to go to bed - did not happen,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 516, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Got to bed at about 3.30am and woke up at 7.30 this morning.\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not get too much sleep but that's not surprising.\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 635, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I watched it (the race) before I went to sleep because I knew I would not sleep so I watched it and I am very happy, it was paced to perfection, that's all we can ask for.\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 809, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Words can not describe how you feel when you wake up and next to your pillow is an Olympic gold medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 915, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gold medal winner Daniel Wiffen speaks to RT\\u00c9 Sport the day after winning gold in the 800m freestyle#RTESport#Paris2024\\ud83d\\udcfa Watchhttps://t.co/b2OI4OoWVJ\\ud83d\\udcf1Updateshttps://t.co/01ShZjM17Cpic.twitter.com/oPd5qDaC0d  Wiffen's family - including his twin brother Nathan - were poolside to witness his stunning victory.\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1172, \"end\": 1178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nathan_Petrelli\", \"score\": 0.9999999999556621, \"rank\": 4.43317330853688e-11, \"text\": \"Nathan\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nathan_Petrelli\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nathan_Petrelli\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"It was amazing to see my twin brother in the crowd, you can not ask for more than that, then my whole family being there.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Words just can not describe, seeing my mum crying and that setting me off.\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1435, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And the national anthem, tears going down my face.\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1486, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have kind of forgotten it because it's gone so quick, but it's so cool.\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My parents have been driving me to 4.30am practice, it's been a relentless journey.\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been doing this since I was at least 12-years-old and they kept doing it for me and they are the reason I am here today.\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1774, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are a massive part, and that's why I say it's never an individual sport, swimming, I have got this whole support network behind me.\\\"\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more:Meet Daniel Wiffen - Ireland's gold medal winning swimmer  Wiffen will now be eyeing more success in the 1500m freestyle, with the heats due to start on Saturday morning.\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 2096, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1949, \"end\": 1956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999944468527, \"rank\": 5.553087745629561e-09, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said he will return to training tonight and temporarily put his 800m win \\\"under the bed\\\".\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2190, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am taking it in my stride, the 1500 is in a couple of days.\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2254, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Today is about getting all the emotions out and then tonight I will get back to training.\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to swim this morning, I miss the pool already.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2400, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am going to refocus, forget about this race, put it under the bed after this morning and I will revisit it when I am finished.\\\"\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2532, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch the 2024 Olympic Games with 14 hours of televised action on RT\\u00c92 and RT\\u00c9 Player each day.\", \"from\": 2534, \"to\": 2629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2602, \"end\": 2606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c92\", \"score\": 0.9994238889060038, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c92\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c92\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c92\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Listen to extensive radio coverage on RT\\u00c9 Radio 1 and 2fm's Game On and follow each moment from Paris on RT\\u00c9.ie, the RT\\u00c9 News app and all RT\\u00c9 digital platforms.\", \"from\": 2631, \"to\": 2791, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2729, \"end\": 2734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999995616236, \"rank\": 4.3848442997176383e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2750, \"end\": 2758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_News_and_Current_Affairs\", \"score\": 0.9356964890387794, \"rank\": 0.061574627460354234, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9 News\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_News_and_Current_Affairs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_News_and_Current_Affairs\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Listen to the daily RT\\u00c9 Sport Olympics Podcast.\", \"from\": 2792, \"to\": 2839, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 2841, \"to\": 2852, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 2943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2880, \"end\": 2903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9993664851268295, \"rank\": 0.0006339164685885233, \"text\": \"Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}, {\"begin\": 2905, \"end\": 2912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999944468527, \"rank\": 5.55308774562956